million ringgit (2.967 million dollars) from 12.783 million shares
valued at 66.664 million ringgit (16.379 million dollars) last
Friday.
</P>
<P>
On a sectoral basis, consumer products accounted for 5.961
million shares traded on the main board, industrial products 7.302
million shares, construction 9.526 million shares,
trading/services 34.959 million shares, infrastructure 761,000
shares, finance 19.989 million shares, hotels 360,000 shares,
properties 10.621 million shares, plantation 3.514 million shares,
