<HEADLINE> Israel's Labor Party Leader Holds Talks With </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 15 (Xinhua) -- Visiting leader of the Israeli
opposition Labor Party Ehud Barak Monday held talks with Egyptian
