<HEADLINE> British Trade Team Arrives In Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, June 15 (Xinhua) -- A 23-member British trade team
Monday arrived in Colombo for a 5-day visit to Sri Lanka.
