trophy with a time of 44 minutes 44.553 seconds followed by
Compatriot Tohru Ukawa with 8.738 seconds behind.
</P>
<P>
Italian Lucio Cecchinello took the 125cc race title by clocking
43 minutes 28.423 seconds while Honda teammate Marco Melandri
finished second and Japan's Hiroyuki Kikuchi, also riding a Honda,
came in third. 
