<HEADLINE> Argentine Sensini Probably Ready for Jamaica Game </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOULOUSE, June 14 (Xinhua) -- Defender Nestor Sensini should be fit
for Argentina's next match against Jamaica despite dislocating his
finger on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
